---
const signs = [
  {
    issue: "A/C Not Cooling Properly",
    description: "If your air conditioner is running but not keeping your home cool, it's time for troubleshooting."
  },
  {
    issue: "Unusual Noises",
    description: "Grinding, rattling, or hissing sounds could indicate a serious mechanical issue."
  },
  {
    issue: "A/C Leaks",
    description: "Water or refrigerant leaks can lead to bigger problems if not addressed quickly."
  },
  {
    issue: "Short Cycling",
    description: "If your A/C turns on and off too frequently, it's wasting energy and reducing efficiency."
  },
  {
    issue: "High Energy Bills",
    description: "A sudden spike in energy costs could mean your system is working harder than it should."
  }
];
---

<section class="mb-16">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Signs You Need A/C Repair</h2>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
    Not sure if it's time to call for professional air conditioning repair in Berks County? Look out for these common issues:
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    {signs.map(sign => (
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">{sign.issue}</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">{sign.description}</p>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>